{"tid":830250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國已封鎖Twitch","createTime":"2018-09-21T04:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T01:29:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":208,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4ef16e2a1cd62c906c101627dcc29581e2bc01","tid":830250,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I1escLVEcD1p9FjqLbkmDg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/d5392c1a0e8ea0915271c755021cfd18\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FI1escLVEcD1p9FjqLbkmDg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fd5392c1a0e8ea0915271c755021cfd18&h=737f32ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從上次 WeGame急撤《魔物獵人：世界》以及遊戲冰河期的消息後，中國這此將矛頭對準了世界最大遊戲實況Twitch，原本在App Store的Twitch全面下架，電腦版本也全部失聯。<br />\n<br />\n由於伺服器在海外導致網路延遲、直播品質欠佳的問題，亞馬遜公司擁有的Twitch原本在中國並沒有多少用戶，同時也長期被中國官方忽視。然而由於央視在今年的亞運會並沒有轉播電競賽事，因此在今年八月底，許多中國網友就利用Twitch來觀看比賽。<br />\n<br />\n這就讓原本乏人問津的Twitch下載量突然飆高，在亞運會當週成長超過23倍，並一躍成為下載排行第三名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lCeHn_lDCa2F8pC24t380w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/e8d1c85a6c88ed30a48dd464b6d402b9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlCeHn_lDCa2F8pC24t380w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fe8d1c85a6c88ed30a48dd464b6d402b9&h=7d79c724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">部分網友本周稍早在微博反應只剩下幾個省份可以連線。（圖片來源：微博截圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n然而突如其來的大量用戶似乎也引起官方的注意，部分中國網友就反應九月之後Twitch就開始無法連線，最後Twitch在美東時間9月20日向外國媒體證實自己已經被中國封鎖並且連帶下架在App Store的Twitch App。不過除此之外，Twitch並沒有更多的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81-%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BD%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E9%87%8F%E6%9A%B4%E8%B5%B7%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0twitch-023619247.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B3%2581-%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%2581%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B3%2581%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0twitch-023619247.html&d=FSuEM9jv38mr8qdJ%2BqezmG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4e1db3df\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81-%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BD%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E9%87%8F%E6%9A%B4%E8%B5%B7%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0twitch-023619247.html</a>"},{"pid":"e8de2dee3bacc85826d3da4df46158c3d5149649","tid":830250,"uid":209337,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"什麼！！真的嗎？"},{"pid":"432109188794fc1abe12ab5a3c85f2715c8231c6","tid":830250,"uid":693,"like":263,"dislike":1,"score":262,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"鎖國啦ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0a63dc17d1198fc686b1349583f2d182d6589c","tid":830250,"uid":106247,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"大陸用開鬥魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人先睇twich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a84b27d4d6497f0ae2137c6e8ee5f056a959ae","tid":830250,"uid":76310,"like":126,"dislike":1,"score":125,"quote":{"pid":"432109188794fc1abe12ab5a3c85f2715c8231c6","tid":830250,"uid":693,"like":263,"dislike":1,"sco